name: THE 504 OF THE PINK PANTHER
description:
Long night for the pink panther, after leaving a clandestine party suspended by a strong wind, when she returns to her car she discovers that things happened ...

Larga noche para la pantera rosa, luego de salir de una fiesta clandestina suspendida por un fuerte viento, cuando regresa a su auto descubre que pasaron cosas ...
